            <title>[OPENJPA-274] JPQL queries cannot access version fields, including bulk updates</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-274</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;OpenJPA throws an exception if a query uses a field mapped as a @Version. This happens because FieldMappings for fields that are @Version do not have any columns, since the columns are managed separately by the owning ClassMapping&apos;s version indicator.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
